===Etymology===
From [[Veglia]], the name of an island where the language was spoken.

===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

#[[pertain|Pertaining]] to the Vegliot dialect or the people who spoke this dialect.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The [[northern]] [[dialect]] of [[Dalmatian]], spoken on the [[island]] of [[Veglia]].
# A person who spoke Vegliot (now extinct).

